We've also introduced Spotlight
on Lock screen and added support

00:02:16.776 --> 00:02:18.976 A:middle
to quickly preview
results with 3D Touch.

00:02:19.746 --> 00:02:21.566 A:middle
That's see what this looks like.

00:02:22.916 --> 00:02:25.596 A:middle
Suppose you're having an
argument with a friend

00:02:25.596 --> 00:02:27.176 A:middle
on where Steph Curry was born.

00:02:27.176 --> 00:02:30.156 A:middle
You can go to the Lock screen,

00:02:31.226 --> 00:02:35.976 A:middle
run your search,

00:02:36.206 --> 00:02:39.136 A:middle
see the result, and now you can
use 3D Touch to preview these --

00:02:44.646 --> 00:02:46.016 A:middle
and find the one you
were looking for,

00:02:46.016 --> 00:02:47.626 A:middle
which is Wikipedia in this case.

00:02:48.566 --> 00:02:49.746 A:middle
Really, really convenient.

00:02:49.746 --> 00:02:52.196 A:middle
And, of course, when you're in
Lock screen, the only results

00:02:52.196 --> 00:02:56.046 A:middle
that you present are public
results from the internet.

