00:02:58.576 --> 00:03:00.536 A:middle
Now, another neat
feature that we've added

00:03:00.536 --> 00:03:03.856 A:middle
to Spotlight is query
suggestions, which appear

00:03:03.856 --> 00:03:06.676 A:middle
in the quick type
area above the keyword

00:03:06.676 --> 00:03:07.816 A:middle
when you type in the query.

00:03:07.816 --> 00:03:09.096 A:middle
Let's look at an example.

00:03:09.716 --> 00:03:11.886 A:middle
Here the user searches
for banjo, and we know,

00:03:11.886 --> 00:03:15.416 A:middle
based on past queries,
that two common completions

00:03:15.416 --> 00:03:18.296 A:middle
for banjo are banjo
chords and banjo tuner.

00:03:18.516 --> 00:03:20.826 A:middle
So if the result that they
are looking for is not already

00:03:20.826 --> 00:03:23.876 A:middle
on the screen, they can pick one
of these and get to the answer.

00:03:23.876 --> 00:03:26.976 A:middle
This will make a lot
of queries a lot faster

00:03:27.116 --> 00:03:28.166 A:middle
to execute in Spotlight.

00:03:28.166 --> 00:03:30.276 A:middle
Now, we've done many
more improvements.

