We've improved spell correction
for the app launch use case.

00:03:34.566 --> 00:03:37.056 A:middle
We've improved support
for Japanese

00:03:37.056 --> 00:03:39.866 A:middle
and Chinese scripts on device.

00:03:39.866 --> 00:03:42.546 A:middle
And we've made relevant,
in general, much better.

00:03:42.546 --> 00:03:44.336 A:middle
And all these changes,
of course,

00:03:44.336 --> 00:03:47.736 A:middle
apply to content that's
inserted while Search APIs.

00:03:49.276 --> 00:03:52.316 A:middle
So now let's turn our
attention to Search APIs.

00:03:53.416 --> 00:03:55.316 A:middle
Now, as many of you
may remember,

00:03:55.316 --> 00:03:58.566 A:middle
we introduced three
Search APIs in iOS 9.

00:03:59.096 --> 00:04:00.806 A:middle
There's CoreSpotlight,
which allows you


WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:03:59.096 --> 00:04:00.806 A:middle
There's CoreSpotlight,
which allows you

00:04:00.806 --> 00:04:04.746 A:middle
to insert user specific or
user created content right

00:04:04.746 --> 00:04:06.616 A:middle
on Spotlight's device index.

00:04:07.836 --> 00:04:09.866 A:middle
We also introduced
NSUserActivity,

00:04:09.866 --> 00:04:13.136 A:middle
a searchable version of this,
that provides an easy way

00:04:13.136 --> 00:04:17.236 A:middle
to index everything that the
user has seen inside of your app

00:04:17.286 --> 00:04:20.255 A:middle
so that they can search for
it and get back to it easily.

00:04:20.255 --> 00:04:24.496 A:middle
And finally, we introduced
a Universal Links index,

00:04:24.786 --> 00:04:28.456 A:middle
which is an index on the
server side consisting of links

00:04:28.656 --> 00:04:32.046 A:middle
that we have discovered
by crawling app websites.

00:04:32.226 --> 00:04:34.226 A:middle
And we designed these
APIs to work in concert,

00:04:34.226 --> 00:04:36.496 A:middle
so whether the results
are coming from the device

00:04:36.676 --> 00:04:39.076 A:middle
or the server, they
blend together

00:04:39.576 --> 00:04:43.466 A:middle
to provide a seamless experience
of searching your app.

00:04:44.636 --> 00:04:48.806 A:middle
I'm happy to announce
that over 50,000 apps

00:04:48.806 --> 00:04:50.626 A:middle
in the App Store have
an app that Search APIs.

00:04:50.786 --> 00:04:51.976 A:middle
It's really incredible.

00:04:52.516 --> 00:04:57.666 A:middle
[ Applause ]

