Now, wikiHow uses
Universal Links

00:08:24.336 --> 00:08:25.966 A:middle
and they have a popular app.

00:08:26.376 --> 00:08:29.236 A:middle
So we have indexed their
articles on the server

00:08:29.436 --> 00:08:33.895 A:middle
and we present them for
appropriate queries.

